    },
    {
      "text": "B16.2.9BROADCASTLIMELISION",
      "bbox": [
        54.0,
        168.82797241210938,
        240.48855590820312,
        179.49256896972656
      ],
      "avg_size": 11.357399940490723,
      "category": "other"
    },
    {
      "text": "The BROADCASTLIMELISION signal is used to control the issuing of elided data messages when theLimited_Data_Elision property is True.",
      "bbox": [
        110.38400268554688,
        194.8118438720703,
        529.7593994140625,
        215.79296875
      ],
      "avg_size": 9.962599754333496,
      "category": "body_text"
    },
    {
      "text": "Table B16.29: BROADCASTLIMELISION pin presence implications",
      "bbox": [
        261.0560302734375,
        233.47265625,
        557.31396484375,
        242.35983276367188
      ],
      "avg_size": 9.464500427246094,
      "category": "table_caption"
    },
    {
      "text": "BROADCASTLIMELISIONDescription",
      "bbox": [
        59.97800064086914,
        260.330810546875,
        291.26971435546875,
        269.2872009277344
      ],
      "avg_size": 9.962599754333496,
      "category": "callout"
    },
    {
      "text": "Not presentThe interface either:",
      "bbox": [
        59.97800064086914,
        279.18035888671875,
        322.6916809082031,
        288.0869140625
      ],
      "avg_size": 9.962599754333496,
      "category": "callout"
    },
    {
      "text": "– Will not issue data messages that make use of the Limited Data Elisionfeature.– Supports the Limited Data Elision feature, but has an alternativemechanism to control the issuing of data messages tha",
      "bbox": [
        253.96697998046875,
        291.1353759765625,
        546.7877807617188,
        347.8619384765625
      ],
      "avg_size": 9.962599754333496,
      "category": "callout"
    },
    {
      "text": "PresentThe interface supports sending and receiving of Limited elision messages.",
      "bbox": [
        59.97800064086914,
        369.24237060546875,
        537.16650390625,
        378.14892578125
      ],
      "avg_size": 9.962599754333496,
      "category": "body_text"
    },
    {
      "text": "When BROADCASTLIMELISION is 0Limited elided messages must notbe sent. This means always havingNumDat and Replicate set to zero.",
      "bbox": [
        247.98899841308594,
        384.82879638671875,
        568.5730590820312,
        417.764892578125
      ],
      "avg_size": 9.962599754333496,
      "category": "body_text"
    },
    {
      "text": "When BROADCASTLIMELISION is 1Limited elided messages arepermitted to be sent. This meansNumDat and Replicate can takenon-zero values, when appropriate.",
      "bbox": [
        247.989013671875,
        426.6717834472656,
        570.0375366210938,
        471.5628662109375
      ],
      "avg_size": 9.962599754333496,
      "category": "body_text"
    },
